{
  "texts": [
    "It is trained on unlabeled text, considering both left and right context in all layers.",
    "BERT undergoes pre-training on two target tasks: masked language modeling and next sentence prediction.",
    "In the context of AES tasks, BERT is used as an initial essay representation module, which is then finetuned on the essay training set.",
    "By introducing an additional layer to BERT, the model parameters can be updated to accommodate the essay scoring training data.",
    "Several research studies utilize fully-connected layer on top of the BERT-encoded essay to generate a score (Yang et al. (2020)"
  ]
}